      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2001 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This specimen features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant, equipped with individual throttle bodies and Double-VANOS variable valve timing, mated to a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox. The mechanical state is superlative: the rear subframe has been reinforced, and the rod bearings have been addressed for long-term reliability. Featuring a Variable M Differential Lock and a perfectly balanced chassis, this M3 provides an unparalleled analog feedback loop. Every component, from the suspension bushings to the cooling system, remains in peak operational status. A truly turn-key example for the discerning enthusiast.",
